      "text": [
        " سَمِعْتُ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَقُولُ: \"مَنْ آمَنَ رَجُلاً عَلَى دَمِهِ، ثُمَّ قَتَلَهُ جَاءَ يَوْمَ اَلْقِيَامَةِ يَحْمِلُ لِوَاءَ اَلْغَدْرِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4943 - Yunus ibn Abd al-Rahman narrated from Abdullah ibn Sulayman, who said: I heard Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) say:\n\"Whoever grants a man safety over his life and then kills him will come on the Day of Judgment carrying the banner of treachery.\""
        ]
      }
    },
